{"tid":1765224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動成效有目共睹，需要轉型","createTime":"2019-12-01T16:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T13:55:20.000Z","uid":197783,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"230527cd71a8ebd05eb6a830c6463a54f022bda7","tid":1765224,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"罷工罷唔到，唔緊要，知道大家要生活要供樓。<br />\n<br />\n有冇可能試下另類方式抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n自我宵禁， 自我戒嚴， 放工後一係食黃店，一係返屋企煮飯， 一蚊多餘錢都唔消費， 盡慳， 盡唔出街.<br />\n<br />\n再進一步可以搞黃色以物易物/捐贈圈子，減少消費，又可以支持環保。<br />\n<br />\n銀行戶口有錢冇所謂，但係職員叫我買保險，買基金，我地就講，「支持黃色經濟.  」婉以拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節依d 重點節日，6點後自我宵禁。 等香港變死城。<br />\n<br />\n大家用消極消費既方法，逼使各行各業，甚至各公會真正支持罷工。"},{"pid":"bcba50649c83db1b0ba82854377d2d68e880e90c","tid":1765224,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"罷買奢侈品係咪一直做緊？"},{"pid":"4cf1d6c9e799cc2911040778fd65862d77259120","tid":1765224,"uid":56305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyGTv5k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyGTv5k.jpg&h=7c115cb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"266c5742a9e970fe205cd82ca2deda385c4aee19","tid":1765224,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"自我宵禁唔可行<br />\n仲有起碼2,3成藍唔會理<br />\n加埋有啲人口講係黃但唔會參與<br />\n今日喺尖沙咀大把人始行街睇戲食飯"},{"pid":"89ee286dd40130170829cae0a617c64ebb2dd4f3","tid":1765224,"uid":245552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"勁，用返屋企煮飯作為抗爭方式<br />\n真係不得不佩服港人創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9329363722cec4f0bac0106912dd209ce7609113","tid":1765224,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"266c5742a9e970fe205cd82ca2deda385c4aee19","tid":1765224,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"自我宵禁唔可行<br />\